graph LR
    MRO[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MRO -->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 16+<br/>postgresql-16-c10s]
    MRO -->|alternative storage| MySQL[MySQL 3306+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    MRO -.->|auth proxy| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>latest]
    MRO -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    MRO -.->|auto TLS certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service Certificates]
    MRO -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio/Service Mesh]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    MRO -->|platform integration| PlatformComponents[components.platform.opendatahub.io<br/>CRD]
    MRO -->|auth discovery| PlatformServices[services.platform.opendatahub.io<br/>CRD - auths]

    %% Core Kubernetes Dependencies
    MRO -->|resource mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>CRD, RBAC, webhooks]
    MRO -.->|external ingress| OpenShiftRouter[OpenShift Router<br/>Routes]

    %% Optional Features
    MRO -.->|curated metadata| ModelCatalog[Model Catalog<br/>optional feature]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| MRO
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|model registration| MRO
    KServe[KServe] -.->|model metadata| MRO
    Users[Data Scientists] -->|CR management| MRO

    %% Model Registry Instance Dependencies
    subgraph "Model Registry Instance (Created by Operator)"
        RestAPI[REST API Service]
        RBACProxySidecar[kube-rbac-proxy sidecar]
        DB[PostgreSQL/MySQL DB]
    end

    MRO -->|provisions| RestAPI
    MRO -->|provisions| RBACProxySidecar
    MRO -->|provisions| DB

    RestAPI -->|stores data| DB
    RBACProxySidecar -->|proxies to| RestAPI
    RBACProxySidecar -->|validates authz| K8sAPI

    %% Styling
    style MRO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    style PostgreSQL fill:#336791,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style MySQL fill:#00758f,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style KubeRBACProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ServiceCA fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    style PlatformComponents fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style PlatformServices fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000

    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OpenShiftRouter fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    style ModelCatalog fill:#d3d3d3,stroke:#333,color:#000

    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Users fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    style RestAPI fill:#6db3f2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style RBACProxySidecar fill:#6db3f2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style DB fill:#336791,stroke:#333,color:#fff
